results.name: Expansion of Product_{k>=1} (1 + x^k - x^(2*k)).
link: Vaclav Kotesovec, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..5000
formula: a(n) ~ sqrt(log(phi)) * phi^sqrt(8*n) / (2^(3/4)*sqrt(Pi)*n^(3/4)), where phi = A001622 = (1+sqrt(5))/2 is the golden ratio. - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Jan 03 2016
